The '''2014 [[China International Challenger]]''' was a professional [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Tennis court#Clay courts|clay courts]]. It was the third edition for men and first edition for women, of the tournament which is part of the [[2014 ATP Challenger Tour]] and the [[2014 ITF Women's Circuit]]. It took place in [[Anning, Yunnan|Anning]], [[China]] between 28 April and 3 May 2014.

