==Champions==
===Singles===
{{main|2014 China International Challenger – Men's Singles}}
* {{flagicon|AUS}} '''[[Alex Bolt]]''' def. {{flagicon|CRO}} [[Nikola Mektić]], 6–2, 7–5

=== Singles ===
{{main|2014 China International Challenger – Women's Singles}}
* {{flagicon|CHN}} '''[[Zheng Saisai]]''' def. {{flagicon|SRB}} [[Jovana Jakšić (tennis)|Jovana Jakšić]] 6–2, 6–3

===Doubles===
{{main|2014 China International Challenger – Men's Doubles}}
*{{flagicon|AUS}} '''[[Alex Bolt]]''' / {{flagicon|AUS}} '''[[Andrew Whittington (tennis)|Andrew Whittington]]''' def. {{flagicon|GRB}} [[Daniel Cox]] / {{flagicon|CHN}} [[Gong Maoxin]], 6–4, 6–3

=== Doubles ===
{{main|2014 China International Challenger – Women's Doubles}}
* {{flagicon|CHN}} '''[[Han Xinyun]]''' / {{flagicon|CHN}} '''[[Zhang Kailin]]''' def. {{flagicon|THA}} [[Varatchaya Wongteanchai]] / {{flagicon|HKG}} [[Zhang Ling (tennis)|Zhang Ling]] 6–4, 6–2

